data.description: Quiet country living on small acreage in the quaint town of Robinson. This lovely home is waiting for you and your family to enjoy small town living! Wonderful open floor plan with kitchen hosting an abundance of cabinets and granite countertops and opens up to the spacious living area with wood burning fireplace, perfect for entertaining. Large game room or second living area upstairs with additional half bath could also be used as a bedroom.  All bedrooms are of ample size and offer tons of storage.  This beautiful home has so many extras you just have to see it. Generous storage building in the fenced in yard. Don't miss out on your own piece of country heaven! Buyers's agent and buyer to verify taxes, square footage and schools.  Information contained in this listing is deemed reliable but is not guaranteed.
